    ImageObserver, MenuContainer, Serializable, Accessible, SolverController, ILogAble, SearchListener<ISolverService>

    public class DetailedCommandPanel
extends JPanel
implements SolverController, SearchListener<ISolverService>, ILogAble
    This panel contains buttons that control restart and clean on solver. It also displays history of commands.
